'''亚伊尔·拉皮德'''（{{lang-he-n|יאיר לפיד}}，{{bd|1963年|11月5日}}），[[以色列|以色列]]政治人物、现任[[以色列总理|以色列总理]]。曾担任[[以色列財政部|以色列財政部部長]]，以色列[[擁有未來|未来党]]主席、[[以色列候補總理|候補總理]]兼[[以色列外交部|外交部長]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=以色列议会投票通过新一届政府组建方案|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-06/14/c_1127560602.htm|access-date=2021-06-29|author=尚昊,吕迎旭|date=2021-06-13|work=|publisher=[[新华社|新华社]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210616191843/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2021-06/14/c_1127560602.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=以色列新政府就职摆脱政治僵局，内塔尼亚胡发誓将很快卷土重来|url=https://www.jiemian.com/article/6229996.html|access-date=2021-06-29|author=田思奇|date=2021-06-14|work=|publisher=[[界面新闻|界面新闻]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629161955/https://www.jiemian.com/article/6229996.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
1963年出生于[[以色列|以色列]][[特拉维夫|特拉维夫]]市，父親出生於南斯拉夫，後來與妻子移民以色列，是一位記者兼政治家[[湯米·拉皮德|湯米·拉皮德]]，曾經擔任司法部長。亚伊尔·拉皮德的父系是匈牙利裔猶太人。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2008-06-27|title=Israel's Archie Bunker took on sacred cows|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/israels-archie-bunker-took-on-sacred-cows-20080627-2y3v.html|access-date=2021-06-24|website=The Sydney Morning Herald|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624212449/https://www.smh.com.au/world/israels-archie-bunker-took-on-sacred-cows-20080627-2y3v.html}}</ref>亚伊尔·拉皮德的曾祖母赫敏·兰佩尔在塞尔维亚被捕并被送往[[奥斯威辛集中营|奥斯威辛集中营]]，最終她在集中營的毒气室遇害<ref>{{cite web | title=The truth about Poland and the Holocaust | url=https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/the-city-of-the-dead/ | publisher=The Times of Israel | year=2018 | access-date=2022-05-06 | archive-date=2021-09-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210904214135/https://blogs.timesofisrael.com/the-city-of-the-dead/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/yairlapid/status/964090139545952256|title=Yair Lapid on Twitter|year=2018|access-date=2022-05-06|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405223121/https://twitter.com/yairlapid/status/964090139545952256}}</ref>。亚伊尔·拉皮德的外祖父是來自羅馬尼亞的德系猶太人。<ref>{{cite web |last=Gradstein |first=Linda |url=http://www.jta.org/news/article/2012/01/17/3091222/in-entering-israeli-politics-yair-lapid-eyes-force-of-socioeconomic-protests |title=In entering Israeli politics, Yair Lapid eyes force of socioeconomic protests | Jewish Telegraphic Agency |website=Jta.org |date=17 January 2012 |access-date=31 March 2016 |archive-date=2013-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130403035142/http://www.jta.org/news/article/2012/01/17/3091222/in-entering-israeli-politics-yair-lapid-eyes-force-of-socioeconomic-protests }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://jwa.org/encyclopedia/article/lapid-shulamit |title=Shulamit Lapid | Jewish Women's Archive |website=Jwa.org |date=1 March 2009 |access-date=31 March 2016 |archive-date=2021-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125135410/https://jwa.org/encyclopedia/article/lapid-shulamit }}</ref>耶爾·拉皮德只是讀到高中就因為[[學習障礙|學習障礙]]而輟學。早年就职于传媒业。2012年4月，组建[[未来党|未来党]]。2013年参加国会选举，他领导的未来党成为以色列第二大党。

